    "description": "WelcomHeritage Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Reservation Manager at our Kochi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout WelcomHeritage Holdings Services:\nWelcomHeritage Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with WelcomHeritage Holdings Services!",
